<p>Drawing from his Good Vibrations technique, Erik can manipulate cursed energy to create powerful vibrations. Whether it is channeling this energy into his strikes for devastating impact or employing it defensively to destabilize opponents, Erik's mastery over this technique enables him to command a unique form of combat.</p>
<p>As he continues his studies and further hones his skills at Kyoto Jujutsu High, Erik Skarsgaard aims to surpass the reputation of his parents and fulfill his destiny as a legendary sorcerer. His journey promises epic battles, formidable alliances, and immense growth as he strives to protect the world from the ever-looming threat of cursed spirits.</p></div>

