<p>Throughout their shared battles against evil, Shiva's presence continues to remind both the Sailor Guardians and their enemies alike that true strength comes not only from physical power, but also from the bonds of friendship, love, and unwavering dedication to justice.</p>
<p>As the Streets of Rage Game Series x Sailor Moon Crossover universe continues to unfold, Shiva's unforgettable journey intertwines with that of Sailor Neptune and the rest of the Sailor Moon cast, ultimately shaping the fate of the universe and proving that even amidst chaos, love and strength can conquer all.</p></div>

