    line-height: 1.6;"> APPLICATION:  Writing About Economics<br/>In 1889, Jane Addams founded the Hull House Association in Chicago to help newly arrived immigrants adjust to the challenges of city life. In 1910, she wrote that “of all the aspects of social misery nothing is so heartbreaking as unemployment.” Write a paragraph explaining the impact of unemployment on immigrants.  <br/></div><br/><br/>LLM response:<br/><div style="
    background-color: #fff3e6;
