ety<br/>Ahmuivn race is militarism, xenophobia, authoritarianism. Patriarchal and traditional society operated under fascist dictatorship, aesthetics mix of Warhammer 40k and Star Wars, blend resemblance of Nazi Germany and Soviet Union. Frenyan religion is dominant in Frenyan Empire, Frenyan priests resembles priests from Warhammer 40k. Surveillance and propaganda.<br/>Frenyan Empire<br/>Frenyan Empire, fascist empire ruled by dictator Isok Khamsich, a capital of Frenyan Empire. Mix of Russian Empire and Nazi Germany, Imperium of Man from Warhammer 40k, Galactic Empire from Star Wars. Isokism is fascist ideology, symbol shape is Juche in left-sided direction and color is blue associated with color of ahmuivn bloods. Racial purity, ahmuivns are superior to humans and other extraterrestrials. Frenyan Empire committed genocides of extraterrestrials, utilizes exterminatus technique from Warhammer 40k to destroy alien homeworlds. Frenyan Empire poses barbaric threat to peace of intergalactic community.<br/>Religion<br/>Ahmuivn named Christ of Frenvek, he founded catholic Frenyan religion resembles Christianity, crucified in equator of Frenya, for our lord of ahmuivns. Frenyan bible forbids astrology, nudities, adulteries, fornications, blasphemies. Pornography, degeneracy, masturbation are violation of religion. Color red is prohibited in religion because it’s associated with sexuality. Marriage is between one husband and one wife.<br/>Military<br/>Military and soldiers are stormtroopers and space marines. Weapons are lightsabers and laser guns. Military vehicles are spaceships and space tanks. Military uniforms are painted with blue, depends color of plants, to camouflage. Frenyan Empire targeted enemies, including heretics, blasphemers, humans, extraterrestrial scum, traitors, witches, and mutants.</div><br/><br/>LLM response:<br/><div style="
